graph TB
    subgraph Component
        TEMPLATE[Template<br/>HTML + Bindings]
        OUTPUT[Event Emitters<br/>Output]
        INPUT[Input Properties<br/>Input]

        TEMPLATE -->|User Action| OUTPUT
        INPUT -->|Data Binding| TEMPLATE
    end

    subgraph ViewModel
        ACTIONS[INPUTS<br/>Methods for actions]
        SIGNALS[OUTPUTS<br/>WritableSignals]
        COMPUTED[OUTPUTS<br/>Computed Signals]
        SUBJECTS[EFFECTS<br/>RxJS Subjects]
        SIDEEFFECTS[EFFECTS<br/>One-time actions]

        ACTIONS -->|Update| SIGNALS
        SIGNALS -.->|Auto-calc| COMPUTED
        ACTIONS -->|Emit| SUBJECTS
        SUBJECTS -->|Subscribe| SIDEEFFECTS
    end

    subgraph Services
        SVC[Domain Services<br/>UserService, etc.]
    end

    OUTPUT -->|Call| ACTIONS
    COMPUTED -->|Subscribe| INPUT
    SIDEEFFECTS -.->|Trigger| TEMPLATE

    ACTIONS -->|Business Logic| SVC
    SVC -.->|Return Data| SIGNALS

